4Geeks Academy offers a course in Applied Artificial Intelligence that explores AI in different industries and roles. The course is designed for professionals who want to leverage AI within their current roles. It covers various topics like generative AI, context, prompts, and models. The course duration is 6 weeks with 2 live online classes per week. The class size is limited to 12 people. Upon completion, participants receive an official 4Geeks Completion Certificate recognized by multiple institutions. No previous experience is required. For more information, visit their website: [https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/applied-ai-course](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/applied-ai-course). stop